org.pepstock.charba.client.data

Class Dataset

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pepstock.charba.client.commons.JavaScriptObjectContainer
      • org.pepstock.charba.client.data.Dataset
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BarDataset, BubbleDataset, LineDataset, PieDataset, PolarAreaDataset, PolarDataset, RadarDataset

    public abstract class Dataset
extends JavaScriptObjectContainer
    The chart allows a number of properties to be specified for each dataset. These are used to set display properties for a specific dataset.
    This is the base implementation for all datasets with common fields.
    Author:
    Andrea "Stock" Stocchero
